posting_body: ['GREAT LOCATION!', 'SUNNY TOP FLOOR 1 BED STEPS TO THE T!', 'HEAT INCLUDED!', '- $1,595 per month', '16 West Wyoming Ave, Melrose, MA 02176', 'FEATURES', 'Bedrooms:', '1', 'Bathrooms:', '1', 'Located on Floor #:', '3', 'Floors in Bldg:', '3', 'DESCRIPTION', 'Located only steps from the Wyoming Hill commuter rail station, and conveniently near the Oak Grove Orange Line T, this sunny top floor corner 1 bedroom apartment features hardwood floors, generously sized living room and bedroom, high ceilings, and lots of windows.', 'Heat and hot water are included.', 'Laundry is on the premises.', 'Available Now or 8/1/2022.', 'RENTAL UNIT AMENITIES', 'Refrigerator', 'Hardwood Floors', 'BUILDING AMENITIES', 'On-site Laundry', 'OTHER PRICING DETAILS', 'Available Date:   Mon Aug 01, 2022', 'Included Utilities:   Heat & Hot Water', 'CONTACT INFO', 'Roy Seidenberg', '617-628-4663 x100', 'Boston Rental Exchange', 'brex10-ry']
